hopobject.body: International directory enquiries myogenix creatine monohydrate review A statement from David Mobbs, chief executive of Nuffield Health – which was recently criticised by HCA for using its charitable status to save on tax – added:Â  “Today’s report should act as a wake-up call for the private healthcare sector. The over-riding need for some providers to make huge profits at the expense of UK patients is clearly evident throughout the report… Our status as a charity, for which we have been criticised by other hospital providers allows us to act free from the demands of shareholders and place greater emphasis on putting patients before profits.”
